    "A decrease in both the mean and median values suggests that the predicted location is in closer proximity to the actual ground truth position.",
    "To quantify the overall performance of programs, the average metrics across all the ligand-target pairs in each dataset have been computed, and represented in Fig. 4 with an \"Average\" label.The results of Fpocket, as a well-known cavity detector, show that the choice of the benchmark can drastically reduce accuracy from 0.78 to 0.38.",
    "Despite the considerable variability in the accuracy of Fpocket, which diminishes its reliability, it is noteworthy that Fpocket achieved the second-highest accuracy score of 0.635 among the programs evaluated in the CASF-2016 assessment.",
